overview.overview: Screego is a screen sharing tool that allows users to share their screens with others over the web.

childMarkdownRemark.html: Screen is designed to be easy to use and set up, often requiring no installation or registration for the participants. Screego can be particularly useful for remote work, online presentations, or collaborative sessions where participants need to share visual information in real-time.
